{"title":"Bites","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"chocolate-bites","title":"Chocolate Bites","description":"","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342019322136,"sku":null,"price":725.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":45342019354904,"sku":null,"price":1450.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":45342019387672,"sku":null,"price":2900.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Chocolate_bites_1.jpg?v=1770649474"},{"product_id":"mango-bites","title":"Mango Bites","description":"","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342049403160,"sku":null,"price":725.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":45342049435928,"sku":null,"price":1450.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":45342049468696,"sku":null,"price":2900.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/bites8_7.png?v=1771688676"},{"product_id":"mewa-bites","title":"Mewa Bites","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"pro-des-title pro-info-box\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eTruly Scrumptious\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eEnjoy the divine taste of Mewa Bite from the pioneers themselves. The premium sweet keeps the Indian taste alive with its exotic preparation. The Mewa bites are cube shaped mithai filled with the crunchiness of dry fruits and nuts in every bite you take. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThis delicacy has a shelf life of 45 days with international standard packing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEach bite is filled with the delightful crunch of almonds, pistachios, cashews, and enhanced with the richness of pure ghee and white chocolate. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePackaged to international standards, these delicacies have a shelf life of 45 days, ensuring freshness in every bite.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAt Dadu's, we ensure that you can shop our premium sweets online with ease.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOur Mewa Bites are delivered to your home with utmost care by our reliable logistics partners.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor international shipping inquiries, contact our support. Our clients within Hyderabad, India can get instant delivery using \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.swiggy.com\/menu\/2085?source=sharing\" style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eSwiggy\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e or \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/zomato.onelink.me\/xqzv\/h1s29802\" style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eZomato\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor a free tasting and a true gourmet experience, visit Dadu’s near you\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"pro-description-box pro-info-box\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cb data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eShelf Life\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e45 \u003c\/span\u003edays from packaging\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cb data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eIngredients\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAlmond, Pistachio, Cashew, Sugar, Ghee, White Chocolate\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cb data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eStorage Instructions\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eStore in a cool and dry place\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342053597464,"sku":null,"price":725.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":45342053630232,"sku":null,"price":1450.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":45342053663000,"sku":null,"price":2900.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/36_6bf848a4-a435-4f32-9c20-c6b9fea29ca7.png?v=1771688881"},{"product_id":"orange-bites","title":"Orange Bites","description":"","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342081646872,"sku":null,"price":725.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":45342081679640,"sku":null,"price":1450.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":45342081712408,"sku":null,"price":2900.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/OrangeBites.jpg?v=1771678153"},{"product_id":"premium-almond-bites","title":"Premium Almond Bites","description":"","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45342564253976,"sku":null,"price":820.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":45342564286744,"sku":null,"price":1640.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"1 Kg","offer_id":45342564319512,"sku":null,"price":3280.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/PremiumBadambites.png?v=1771678320"},{"product_id":"rose-bites","title":"Rose Bites","description":""